2020 will be my year. New goals to accomplish. Different year, Different me. Learn as you evolve. The mistakes you made in the past is telling you to do better. I am all pure now. All that hate I left in the past. Still, I’m not done writing the chapter in my book. I will respond to hate every now and then but all that fighting and stuff is just for babies. Sorry for the late reply and happy 2020 to you all......enjoy!

Basically if I give a fuck, then they won’t but if I don’t then they do. Oh well, life sucks for most people, I don’t believe in happy endings, I don’t believe in marriage so that’s gone down the drain. I heard everybody gets married but looks like half of the world are either sniffing crack or there being too picky. Every time you look at the picture, just say, “wow, he really don’t give a fuck”
